N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 35.3 - Privileges granted by permit

State Regulations
A permit shall allow on premises licensees to serve
alcoholic beverages between the hours of 4 a.m., or the closing hour proscribed
in the licensee's county, and 8 a.m. Notes
